sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant ShareExtension
    participant System

    User->>ShareExtension: Initiate share
    ShareExtension->>System: Request sharing options
    System-->>ShareExtension: Provide sharing options
    ShareExtension-->>User: Display sharing options
    User->>ShareExtension: Select sharing option
    ShareExtension->>System: Send shared content
    System-->>ShareExtension: Confirm receipt
    ShareExtension-->>User: Notify sharing success